  "3059010": {
    "name": "二战前线合集",
    "steam_appid": 3059010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/892b540c30dba35d135558830a61a366.avif?t=1770370308\" width=590 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本合集是一个持续扩展的游戏库。除了包含核心作品《二战前线2》、《二战前线X》和《二战前线3》之外，我们将不断把 Macrojoy 的海量经典游戏引入其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我们会对每一款入库的游戏进行精心打磨，包括：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>画面高清化：</strong> 让经典像素焕发新生。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>难度调整：</strong> 优化游戏平衡，改善体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>技术升级：</strong> 顺应时代要求，完美适配现代操作系统与操作习惯。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/1fde2b1662f1fea0d0ca32b57054092f.avif?t=1770370308\" width=1450 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1，二战前线2</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/e9b2885b636c0e0bdcb70603b1cf5abd.avif?t=1770370308\" width=1450 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作在本次合集中得到了全面优化，追加了更多种类的敌人，丰富了关卡设计，还添加了全新的创意工坊系统，高清化了图像，平衡了游戏难度，并调整了部分Boss的AI。此外，游戏还增加了许多有趣的音效，让玩家的游戏体验更加生动。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/aa07d1ad4fc143f54f0bf217769c3378.poster.avif?t=1770370308\" width=590 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/aa07d1ad4fc143f54f0bf217769c3378.webm?t=1770370308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/aa07d1ad4fc143f54f0bf217769c3378.mp4?t=1770370308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入游戏后，您可以在左上角的设置界面找到丰富的自定义选项，如敌人生成倍率、BOSS召唤部队和血液效果个性化调节。通过这些设置，您将体验到与儿时截然不同的游戏乐趣，迎战如潮水般涌来的敌军，感受横扫千军的极致爽快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/05f69a5c668a225db88152ac17eb8b27.poster.avif?t=1770370308\" width=590 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/05f69a5c668a225db88152ac17eb8b27.webm?t=1770370308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/05f69a5c668a225db88152ac17eb8b27.mp4?t=1770370308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2，二战前线X突击对决</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/b8de889ea4f0b8219abeff0a613dfc5f.avif?t=1770370308\" width=1450 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为《二战前线2》的分支作品，玩家在本作中将与敌军展开阵地对攻，体验与2代完全不同的集团作战模式。与《二战前线2》一样，本作也进行了全面优化，带来了更好的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3，二战前线3</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/48e53f4b71cb8a24f6f6d323ade0f470.avif?t=1770370308\" width=1450 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为《二战前线2》的续作，本作增加了丰富的坐骑系统，更多的敌人类型和战斗场景，同时，游戏的绘画风格从Q版转变为更偏向写实的风格，为玩家带来了更为真实的战争体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4，特别赠送部分（Macrojoy追加游戏合集）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/5d1a830e2787a4b9e3474bd17eaedef6.avif?t=1770370308\" width=1450 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/600902aa75e4cedb752d501022a8aa23.avif?t=1770370308\" width=1450 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/70a847c2c2301e65e1285237ac6baf95.avif?t=1770370308\" width=1450 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>2025年12月，Macrojoy补完计划正式启动！ 我们将在“特别赠送”页面的右侧栏目中持续追加新游戏，致力于让这个合集的内容越来越丰富。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这部分还包含了《二战前线2》的小MV、扫描版设计稿、全体演员的谢幕动画以及该系列未来计划的介绍。这些特别内容为玩家提供了更多游戏之外的乐趣和期待。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059010/extras/0a44a6694f6da30f718d7888eb15233a.avif?t=1770370308\" width=1450 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是系列的老玩家还是新手，《二战前线合集》都将带给你空前激烈的战斗和丰富的游戏体验。准备好，踏上二战的战场，体验战斗的激情吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏部分封面图与宣传插图由 AI 工具基于本游戏的原创角色生成，仅用于宣传展示。</p>",
